SlashStrike thinks this statement over. "I WAS a maximal. Currently I am of 
NO faction, but I have done nothing to support or betray either side." He 
wonders if she should be so honest. To show that he means no harm, he sheaths 
his sword into his back. "I... am here to assist those in the right."

--part1_9.e241fa7.27657f34_boundary
